@page
@model ChatbotModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Pelé ChatBot";
}

@section Styles {
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="~/css/bots.css" asp-append-version="true" />
}

<div class="page-spacer chatbot-page">

    <section class="section-card mb-4 text-center">
        <h1 class="hero-title">JerseyNation Pelé - AI Assistant</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle chatbot-intro">
            Pelé is JerseyNation's shopping assistant. Built with Botpress, it helps customers explore jerseys,
            compare products, understand policies, check delivery timing, and connect purchases to the 2026 World Cup schedule.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap gap-2 chatbot-actions">
            <a href="/docs/Pele_SYSTEM_PROMPT_v5.txt" class="btn btn-outline-primary" target="_blank">ShopBot Configuration</a>
            <a asp-page="/ChatBot2" class="btn btn-outline-light">Admin ChatBot</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card mb-4">
        <h2>About the ChatBot</h2>
        <p>
            Pelé is the customer-facing AI assistant created for JerseyNation. It was designed to support users during the shopping
            journey and answer questions about official national team jerseys featured on the website.
        </p>
        <p>
            The ChatBot can help with product recommendations, prices, sizes, premium items, shipping, delivery timing, store policies,
            authenticity, and other common support questions. It also uses World Cup match information so users can connect jerseys with
            upcoming games, teams, and locations.
        </p>
        <p class="mb-0">
            While Maradona focuses on project and analytical support, Pele is centered on customer service, sales guidance, and a more
            engaging shopping experience.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card mb-4">
        <h2>Pages Where Pelé Is Active</h2>
        <p class="mb-3">Pelé appears in customer-facing sections of the website to guide browsing, shopping, and product decisions.</p>
        <div class="row chatbot-grid-3">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <a asp-page="/Index" class="pages-card-link">
                    <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                        <div class="chatbot-icon">🏠</div>
                        <h3>Home</h3>
                        <p>Project overview, featured highlights, and first contact with the shopping assistant.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <a asp-page="/Shop" class="pages-card-link">
                    <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                        <div class="chatbot-icon">🛍️</div>
                        <h3>Shop</h3>
                        <p>Catalog browsing, product filtering, recommendations, and product-related questions.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <a asp-page="/ProductDetails" asp-route-id="1" class="pages-card-link">
                    <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                        <div class="chatbot-icon">📦</div>
                        <h3>Product Details</h3>
                        <p>Help with sizes, pricing, delivery expectations, and purchase confidence.</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card mb-4">
        <h2>Data Used by Pelé</h2>
        <p>
            Pele uses structured product and World Cup data prepared for the project and converted into a Botpress knowledge base.
            The ChatBot uses these records to answer customer questions with consistent and focused responses.
        </p>
        <div class="row g-4 mt-1">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Main product data</h3>
                <ul class="chatbot-data-list">
                    <li>Product ID, product name, team, category, and price</li>
                    <li>Audience, size availability, premium status, and special features</li>
                    <li>Collector items such as signed and match-worn jerseys</li>
                    <li>Promotional prices and catalog highlights</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h3>Main World Cup data</h3>
                <ul class="chatbot-data-list">
                    <li>Match date, teams, host city, and stadium context</li>
                    <li>Connections between store teams and upcoming games</li>
                    <li>Schedule-based answers for delivery and gift planning</li>
                    <li>Support for shopping questions tied to specific matches</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="chatbot-note mt-3 mb-3">Below are 5 example rows from each table used in the knowledge base.</p>

        <h3 class="mb-2">Product catalog — 5 example rows</h3>
        <div class="table-responsive mb-4">
            <table class="table align-middle chatbot-data-table mb-0">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>ID</th>
                        <th>Product</th>
                        <th>Team</th>
                        <th>Category</th>
                        <th>Price</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr><td>P001</td><td>Brazil Home Jersey 2026</td><td>Brazil</td><td>Standard</td><td>$99.99</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>P002</td><td>Argentina 2026 Home Jersey</td><td>Argentina</td><td>Best Seller</td><td>$79.99</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>P003</td><td>France Away Jersey 2026</td><td>France</td><td>Standard</td><td>$95.99</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>P004</td><td>Brazil Signed 2026 Home</td><td>Brazil</td><td>Signed / COA</td><td>$229.99</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>P005</td><td>England Match-Worn Jersey</td><td>England</td><td>Match-Worn</td><td>$1,499.99</td></tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>

        <h3 class="mb-2">World Cup schedule — 5 example rows</h3>
        <div class="table-responsive">
            <table class="table align-middle chatbot-data-table mb-0">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Date</th>
                        <th>Match</th>
                        <th>Location</th>
                        <th>Use in chatbot</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr><td>June 13, 2026</td><td>Brazil vs Morocco</td><td>New York / New Jersey</td><td>Delivery and Brazil jersey questions</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>June 16, 2026</td><td>Argentina vs Algeria</td><td>Kansas City</td><td>Argentina product recommendations</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>June 17, 2026</td><td>England vs Croatia</td><td>Dallas</td><td>England jersey and timing questions</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>June 19, 2026</td><td>Brazil vs Haiti</td><td>Philadelphia</td><td>Follow-up Brazil schedule questions</td></tr>
                    <tr><td>June 27, 2026</td><td>Panama vs England</td><td>New York / New Jersey</td><td>England support and gifting context</td></tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card mb-4">
        <h2 class="mb-3">What You Can Ask</h2>
        <div class="row chatbot-grid-3">
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                    <div class="chatbot-icon">👕</div>
                    <h3>Products and pricing</h3>
                    <p>Ask about available jerseys, prices, categories, premium pieces, and team-specific products.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                    <div class="chatbot-icon">🚚</div>
                    <h3>Shipping and delivery</h3>
                    <p>Ask whether an order can arrive before a match, dispatch timing, express shipping, and delivery guidance.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                    <div class="chatbot-icon">🔄</div>
                    <h3>Returns and policies</h3>
                    <p>Ask about exchanges, refunds, international shipping, payment methods, and store support details.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                    <div class="chatbot-icon">⚽</div>
                    <h3>World Cup matches</h3>
                    <p>Ask about match dates, opponents, host cities, timing, and schedule details for featured teams.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                    <div class="chatbot-icon">🎁</div>
                    <h3>Recommendations</h3>
                    <p>Ask for suggestions by team, budget, collector profile, gift purpose, or upcoming match.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-4">
                <div class="section-card chatbot-mini-card mb-0">
                    <div class="chatbot-icon">📜</div>
                    <h3>Authenticity and support</h3>
                    <p>Ask about signed items, certificates of authenticity, product legitimacy, and common support questions.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card mb-4">
        <h2>Suggested Questions</h2>
        <div class="row g-4 mt-1">
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="sq-label">Shopping</div>
                <ul class="sq-list">
                    <li>Do you have Brazil jerseys in size L?</li>
                    <li>What is your cheapest jersey on promotion?</li>
                    <li>Which jersey would you recommend for a gift?</li>
                    <li>Do you have any signed or match-worn products?</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
                <div class="sq-label">Delivery and World Cup</div>
                <ul class="sq-list">
                    <li>If I buy now, will it arrive before Brazil's next match?</li>
                    <li>When is Argentina's next World Cup game?</li>
                    <li>Do you offer international shipping?</li>
                    <li>What is your return policy if the jersey does not fit?</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card mb-4">
        <h2>Example Conversations</h2>
        <p class="mb-2">Click one of the sample questions to view the full conversation example.</p>

        <div class="chatbot-question-grid" id="pele-question-grid">
            <button type="button" class="chatbot-question-btn active" data-target="pele-convo-1">Will the Brazil jersey arrive before the next match?</button>
            <button type="button" class="chatbot-question-btn" data-target="pele-convo-2">What sizes do you have for the Brazil away jersey?</button>
            <button type="button" class="chatbot-question-btn" data-target="pele-convo-3">When is Argentina's next game?</button>
            <button type="button" class="chatbot-question-btn" data-target="pele-convo-4">What do you recommend as a Brazil gift?</button>
        </div>

        <div class="chatbot-conversation-box">
            <div id="pele-convo-1" class="chatbot-conversation active">
                <div class="chatbot-role">⚽ Pelé</div>
                <p><strong>User:</strong> If I buy the Brazilian jersey today, will I receive it before their next game?</p>
                <p><strong>Pelé:</strong> Yes, you should receive it well before the match, just place your order soon and you're all set. ✅</p>
                <p>Brazil's next game is <strong>June 13, 2026 against Morocco</strong> at MetLife Stadium in New York / New Jersey, with kickoff at 6:00 PM local time and 7:00 PM Brasília time.</p>
                <p>Today is April 17, 2026, so there are still 57 days until the match. Orders are dispatched within 1 business day, so standard shipping should arrive with plenty of time to spare.</p>
                <p>You'll be ready to cheer for Brazil with time to spare. ⚽</p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Brazil 2026 Away Jersey</strong><br />Price: $94.99 (was $104.99)</p>
                <p>Our best-selling Brazil away jersey is available in S, M, L, and XL.</p>
                <p class="mb-0">Would you like to see the signed edition with Vini Jr, Neymar, and Enderson? 🏆</p>
            </div>

            <div id="pele-convo-2" class="chatbot-conversation">
                <div class="chatbot-role">⚽ Pelé</div>
                <p><strong>User:</strong> What sizes do you have for the Brazil away jersey?</p>
                <p><strong>Pelé:</strong> The Brazil 2026 Away Jersey is available in <strong>S, M, L, and XL</strong>. 👕</p>
                <p>If you are looking for something more special, the signed edition comes in M, L, and XL and includes a Certificate of Authenticity.</p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Brazil Signed 2026 Home Jersey</strong><br />Price: $229.99 (was $259.99)</p>
                <p>This premium version is ideal for collectors or as a memorable gift.</p>
                <p class="mb-0">Would you like more details on the signed version, or are you ready to pick a size?</p>
            </div>

            <div id="pele-convo-3" class="chatbot-conversation">
                <div class="chatbot-role">🏆 World Cup</div>
                <p><strong>User:</strong> When is Argentina's next game?</p>
                <p><strong>Pelé:</strong> Argentina's next match is <strong>June 16, 2026 against Algeria</strong> at Arrowhead Stadium in Kansas City, with kickoff at 8:00 PM local time and 10:00 PM Brasília time.</p>
                <p>Since you are asking about Argentina, you may also want to support them with our most popular jersey before the match.</p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Argentina 2026 Home Jersey</strong><br />Price: $79.99 (was $94.99)</p>
                <p>This is one of our best-selling jerseys and is available in S, M, and L.</p>
                <p class="mb-0">Would you like to see our premium Argentina match-worn edition as well?</p>
            </div>

            <div id="pele-convo-4" class="chatbot-conversation">
                <div class="chatbot-role">⚽ Pelé</div>
                <p><strong>User:</strong> I want to give a jersey as a gift for someone who loves Brazil. What do you recommend?</p>
                <p><strong>Pelé:</strong> That is a great gift idea. For a truly memorable option, I would recommend the signed collector's edition. 🇧🇷</p>
                <p>It is signed by <strong>Vini Jr, Neymar, and Enderson</strong>, includes a Certificate of Authenticity, and comes from the premium collection.</p>
                <p class="mb-2"><strong>Brazil Signed 2026 Home Jersey</strong><br />Price: $229.99 (was $259.99)</p>
                <p>It is one of the strongest gift options in the store, especially ahead of the World Cup.</p>
                <p class="mb-0">Do you know the person's size, or would you prefer a standard jersey at a lower price point?</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-card text-center">
        <h2>Try the ChatBot</h2>
        <p class="chatbot-intro mb-3">
            Use the chat icon in the corner of the screen to open Pelé and start asking questions about jerseys,
            prices, delivery timing, store policies, and the World Cup schedule.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center flex-wrap gap-2 chatbot-actions">
            <a href="/docs/Pele_SYSTEM_PROMPT_v5.txt" class="btn btn-outline-primary" target="_blank">ShopBot Configuration</a>
            <a asp-page="/ChatBot2" class="btn btn-outline-light">Admin ChatBot</a>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
</div>

<script>
    (function () {
        const buttons = document.querySelectorAll('#pele-question-grid .chatbot-question-btn');
        const conversations = document.querySelectorAll('.chatbot-conversation');

        buttons.forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener('click', function () {
                const targetId = this.getAttribute('data-target');

                buttons.forEach(btn => btn.classList.remove('active'));
                conversations.forEach(item => item.classList.remove('active'));

                this.classList.add('active');
                const target = document.getElementById(targetId);
                if (target) target.classList.add('active');
            });
        });
    })();
</script>

<script src="https://cdn.botpress.cloud/webchat/v3.6/inject.js"></script>
<script src="https://files.bpcontent.cloud/2026/04/12/04/20260412044811-2GZKX0NN.js" defer></script>
